{"view":"article","slug":"cuberoot-logo","category":"魔方根","subcategory":null,"topDir":"魔方根","title":{"en":"CubeRoot Logo"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong>CubeRoot Logo</strong></p><p>魔方根中文字: </p><p><strong>匚凵㠯巨尺口囗丅</strong></p><p><strong>魇万桹</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>CubeRoot</strong></p><p>💠Scan and Join💠</p><p>WeChat Official Account</p><p>Best Speedcubing Algorithms</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>魔方根</strong></p><p>💠分享魔方公式和解法💠</p><p>微信扫描二维码, 关注我的公众号</p><p><img alt=\"QR 代码\n\n描述已自动生成\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image8.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>扫码并回复\"魔方根\"进入魔方交流群后</p><p>看群公告获取更多魔方教程公式资源</p><p>B站/抖音: 魔方根, Q群153054566</p><p>官网https://cuberoot.me</p><p>加微信mofanggen发你相关资料. 添加后回复\"魔方根\"即可进入魔方根微信群, 讨论有关各种魔方的公式/教程/硬件.</p><p>点击本页面左下角可进入菜单查找内容, 也可点击右上角的人头再点击放大镜搜索推送.</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>魔方根</strong></p><p><a id=\"_Hlk104850449\"></a>国内专业免费魔方公式教程库平台</p><p>微信扫一下这颗37阶魔方💠关注</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><a id=\"_Hlk504420633\"></a><a id=\"_Hlk504325638\"></a><a id=\"_Hlk518657049\"></a><a id=\"_Hlk518380852\"></a><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/cuberoot-logo/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td col